  areaName: Egor Snowfield
  backgroundName: dungeon_battle_10300
  dungeons:
  - dungeonName: 'The Dragon Hunting Ice Knight '
    dungeonDescription: The end of this cold snow field has come into view at last.
      However, it seems one of Maxwell's knights is waiting just ahead. (Dialogue)
  - dungeonName: 'The Pirate on Ice '
    dungeonDescription: You've reached the center of the icy field. Beware, apparently
      there are pirates about on the ice...
  - dungeonName: Manipulator of the Water
    dungeonDescription: You are making progress, but the end of the snowscape still
      isn't visible. Don't forget to plan for water enemies.
  - dungeonName: 'Breath Freezing Snowfields '
    dungeonDescription: You've emerged into a blizzard. It's so cold, watch out for
      enemies with water attacks
